::DarkMouse::

She walked outside and noticed it was getting dark out.  The sun was a few 
hours from setting and Scorponok hadn't returned from the old Predacin base.

She hailed Quickstrike on his commlink.
"Hey, Quickstrike,  this is DarkMouse.  Have you seen Scorponok lately? He 
has been gone hours and not returned form the old Pred base yet.  I wonder 
if he is hurt or ran into one of the unfriendly's.  If you see him, tell him 
I need his help on some of the computer systems will ya."

She waited for Quickstrike to respond.  She stood at the main enterance to 
the cave.  The wind was just barely blowing and the sky was starting to 
darken in the east.  She hoped that the others would return to the cave 
before dark so she could arm the auto-defence systems.
